# Silver Knight Archer Skip (SKAS)

**Silver Knight Archer Skip** is a skip that **allows** you to reach [Ornstein](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/dragon-slayer-ornstein-executioner-smough) & [Smough ](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/dragon-slayer-ornstein-executioner-smough)without having to deal with the **Silver Knight archers**. It also **allows** you to get to the [Giant **Blacksmith**](http://darksouls.wikidot.com/giant-blacksmith) very quickly and reach **O&S** faster than usual.

You can not perform this skip in Glitchless categories of the game.

